<p><em>救助小队沿路行进约30秒。</em></p>



<div class="scp-image-block block-right scp-clear-true" style="width:240px;"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-1777-jp/1777JP1.jpg" style="width:240px;" class="enlarge" alt="1777JP1.jpg" />
